        "short_description": "Insurgency: Sandstorm is a hardcore tactical FPS built on lethal close-quarters combat and ruthless intensity. Every bullet count, every step matters, and teamwork is your only path to survival in the brutality of modern warfare.",
        "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Edition</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/d0221890237e41684a08707853cf37be.avif?t=1779984920\" width=780 height=1576 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/71f77b06fd0843276a7c11e13c4e74ad.poster.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/71f77b06fd0843276a7c11e13c4e74ad.webm?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/71f77b06fd0843276a7c11e13c4e74ad.mp4?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/093979edb5323ca0bcc9dbc4cc1f43fd.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1560 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Insurgency: Sandstorm delivers hardcore tactical combat where death is instant, ammunition is precious, and victory demands skill and coordination. Experience modern warfare's raw brutality through deadly ballistics, devastating artillery strikes, light attack vehicles, and HDR audio that puts the fear back into combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/8c057c1031c5e67d35afe7f90846453c.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1560 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/9566723f1d31082be91afe5dc9800c35.poster.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/9566723f1d31082be91afe5dc9800c35.webm?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/9566723f1d31082be91afe5dc9800c35.mp4?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push through war-torn streets, secure objectives, and survive lethal firefights. With no crosshair, minimal HUD, and realistic damage, every engagement demands tactical awareness and precision. Manage your ammunition carefully, use cover wisely, and coordinate with your squad—because in Sandstorm, there are no second chances.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/c34568e32d01eb38c41de6ed97fef693.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1560 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/f69ce90fe18a30bd2f04091e976d4227.poster.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/f69ce90fe18a30bd2f04091e976d4227.webm?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/f69ce90fe18a30bd2f04091e976d4227.mp4?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modern combat rewards those who communicate and adapt. Choose from specialized classes, coordinate devastating support strikes with your spotter, and respond to constantly shifting frontlines. Individual skill matters, but teamwork wins the fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/7cca5baaf06b4b6d1806e493d007e16b.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1560 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/1869932fda9d03181a39f49d0495ebd6.poster.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/1869932fda9d03181a39f49d0495ebd6.webm?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/1869932fda9d03181a39f49d0495ebd6.mp4?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle in intense PvP matches with up to 14v14 players or face relentless AI in co-op missions that demand tactical precision and squad coordination. Whether you prefer competitive firefights or cooperative survival under pressure, Sandstorm delivers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/5975173738b1f642719b6e88d51c2efb.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1560 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/a5914cced63321d95413b82a79537aff.poster.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/a5914cced63321d95413b82a79537aff.webm?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/a5914cced63321d95413b82a79537aff.mp4?t=1779984920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Powered by gritty visuals and an unmatched soundscape, the chaos of combat comes alive without clutter or distraction. This isn't your typical shooter—this is war as it truly is: brutal, ruthless, and unforgettable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/581320/extras/d77d15cfe206973ab83e2cf57924011b.avif?t=1779984920\" width=1560 height=171 /></span> </p>",
